New Features and Important Changes in ctools 1.0.1

Author(s) : Juergen Knoedlseder

20 December 2015


1. Introduction
---------------
This document briefly summarizes executable by executable the most important
changes made since the last release of ctools. The code complies to ctools
version 1.0.1 or above.


